body:
Comment 9: 
I can't reproduce your problem. And I have no good ideas where to look. The only thing
that looks suspicious in your setup is your GOTOOLDIR value - mine is
GOTOOLDIR=c:\go\pkg\tool\windows_386.

The only good suggestion I have is for you to look at gotour program itself, to see
where and why it breaks. You should be able to put print statements to make sure all
code is executed as expected.

Leaving it for others.

Alex
_Status changed to **Accepted**._
